comment on column SYS.USER_AUDIT_TRAIL.ECONTEXT_ID is 'Execution Context Identifier for each action'
/

comment on column SYS.USER_AUDIT_TRAIL.SESSION_CPU is 'Amount of cpu time used by each Oracle session'
/

comment on column SYS.USER_AUDIT_TRAIL.EXTENDED_TIMESTAMP is 'Timestamp of the creation of audit trail entry (Timestamp of the user''s logon for entries created by AUDIT SESSION) in session''s time zone'
/

comment on column SYS.USER_AUDIT_TRAIL.PROXY_SESSIONID is 'Proxy session serial number, if enterprise user has logged through proxy mechanism'
